In the short clip Babes can be heard mocking Lady Zamar while zooming in to show the acne on her face. * Editor's note: Please be aware the video attached contains graphic language. JOHANNESBURG - Babes Wodumo, real name Bongekile Simelane, is being dragged on social media following a video of her making fun of Lady Zamar's acne went viral. In the short clip, Babes can be heard mocking Lady Zamar while zooming in to show the acne on her face. WATCH: Babes Wodumo, Mampintsha release new song Lady Zamar was a guest judge on Idols when the video was taken. Several people on social media have called out Babes for her comments and insist she was out of line.